nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Ugly old woman with raised hands with white hair and long nose maniacaly laughing and making witch gestures. Behind her in lower roght vorner we see bronze cat figurine.
1. In the beginnong she sits with raised hands for two sides of the frame.
2. Then she raise her hands and clap
3. Then she hold her head.

She in surrounded by old market surrounded with oriental ornamental carpets which are moving with the wind. Heavy wing moving her hair.

Analog video with frontal light with textures and colors and costumes by Emile Nolde depicting.
